text: Annemarie Haensch was a German international table tennis player. ==Table tennis career== She won a gold medal in the team event at the 1934 World Table Tennis Championships for Germany, with Anita Felguth, Astrid Krebsbach and Mona Rüster Muller. ==See also== * List of table tennis players * List of World Table Tennis Championships medalists ==References== Category:German female table tennis players Category:World Table Tennis Championships medalists
title: Annemarie Haensch
